summary: This is an email from December 13, 2021, forwarding a PDF attachment titled '2021.12.10_Letter to_Government_re_Defense_Witness_List_and_26.2_Disclosure.PDF'. The email is addressed to a detective on the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force, indicating legal disclosure related to a defense witness list in an ongoing case.

events.title: Defense Letter to Government Regarding Witness List
events.description: A letter was sent from the defense to the government disclosing a witness list and information under Rule 26.2 of the Federal Rules of Criminal Procedure.
